2008-02-25  Philippe Rouquier  <philippr@svn.gnome.org>

	Fix #510480 – Migrate from GnomeVFS to GIO
	Removed GnomeVFS dependency. Now brasero uses Gio and requires glib 2.15.5 at least
	Some memleaks fixed.
	Fixed crash (division by 0)

