	Denis Leroy <denis@poolshark.org>. Closes bgo #395594.
	
2007-01-11  Luis Medinas  <metalgod@gentoo.org>

	* src/burn-dialog.c: (brasero_burn_dialog_show_log):

	Change logs size to 1MB that is enough fixes bgo # 377198

